steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Web editor" with submenu "Web editor"
Then I should see Web Editor screen display
When I select tab list with name "Pages"
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new page in web editor with name "invalid_JIT001aWebPage!#$%^;" & slug "empty"
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Special characters are not allowed"
When I close the modal popup
When I add new page in web editor with name "empty" & slug "empty"
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Name is required"
Then I should see popup has error message with content "Slug is required"
When I close the modal popup
When I add new page in web editor with name "JIT001aWebPage" & slug "/JIT001aWebPage/slug"
Then I should see the page in web editor with name "JIT001aWebPage" & slug "/JIT001aWebPage/slug" display in list "Pages"
